Echenique-Elizondo, Miguel
Blanco, José Luis
metadata.dc:description: The causes of drug resistance in tumor cells vary widely. The present study aims to provide an update of multidrug resistance in tumor cells and, in particular, of multidrug resistance-associated proteins.
metadata.dc:title: Expresión de proteínas relacionadas con resistencia a múltiples fármacos (MDR-proteínas) en tumores sólidos.
[Expression of multidrug resistance (MDR)-associated proteins in solid tumors].
